    "We ran further analysis to identify which of these 4 categories and their exclusive combinations are seen in these 174 sentences.",
    "We also mapped these on an histogram across the entire manuscript.",
    "The sentences in the dataset are in the order in which the manuscript was originally written.",
    "We grouped the sentences into bins of 25 sentences and colored the histogram bins based on exclusive combinations of harm categories observed in that 25 sentence chunk.",
    "We ran the same translation prompt on the German translation of the manuscript and followed the same model of doing 2 passes."
